data.description:
Nestled in the heart of Greensboro, this delightful spacious 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless charm. This property is ideal for families seeking a welcoming retreat.

Upon entering, you are greeted with natural light that accentuates the warm tones of the hardwood floors. The adjacent kitchen boasts ample cabinet space, sleek countertops, and modern appliances, making it a haven for culinary enthusiasts. The home has a new refrigerator, dishwasher, disposal, kitchen and bathroom faucets, bathroom fans, dining room and eat in kitchen lights, smoke and CO detectors

Step outside to discover the backyard overlooking a community park which gives the feeling of a much larger lot. Don't forget the brand new deck ideal for entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars. The attached garage provides convenient parking and storage space.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming property your new home!
